{"name": "odoo12-addon-account-brand", "metadata": {"name": "odoo12-addon-account-brand", "version": "12.0.3.1.1", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Framework :: Odoo", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/account-invoicing", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo12-addon-analytic-brand", "odoo12-addon-brand", "odoo"], "summary": "Send branded invoices and refunds", "upload_time": 1622638836}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fbrand-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/brand\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/brand/tree/12.0/account_brand\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/brand-12-0/brand-12-0-account_brand\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runbot-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runbot\n    :target: https://runbot.odoo-community.org/runbot/284/12.0\n    ```\n  maintainer-osi-scampbell: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/osi-scampbell.png?size=40px\n    :alt: osi-scampbell\n    :target: https://github.com/osi-scampbell\n    ```\n---\n\n# Account Brand\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module allows you to send branded invoices to your customers.\nIt adds a brand field on the invoice and the brand information to the PDF\nreport.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\nTo configure this module, please refer to the documentation of\n[brand](https://github.com/OCA/brand/blob/12.0/brand/README.rst).\n\n## Usage\n\nTo use this module, you need to:\n\n1. Go to Accounting > Customers > Invoices\n2. Select or create an invoice\n3. Enter the information and select the brand\n4. Print the PDF report. It includes the information of the brand.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/brand/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/brand/issues/new?body=module:%20account_brand%0Aversion:%2012.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Open Source Integrators\n- ACSONE SA/NV\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Raphael Lee \\<<mailto:rlee@opensourceintegrators.com>>\n- Steve Campbell \\<<mailto:scampbell@opensourceintegrators.com>>\n- Maxime Chambreuil \\<<mailto:mchambreuil@opensourceintegrators.com>>\n\n### Other credits\n\n- Open Source Integrators \\<<https://www.opensourceintegrators.com>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainer](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-osi-scampbell }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/brand](https://github.com/OCA/brand/tree/12.0/account_brand) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_brand.models", "documentation": ["Copyright (C) 2019 Open Source Integrators", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_brand.models.account_invoice", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.account_brand.models..account_invoice", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_brand.models.res_partner_account_brand", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.account_brand.models..res_partner_account_brand", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_brand.migrations.12.0.2.0.0.post-migration", "documentation": ["Copyright 2019 ACSONE SA/NV", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_brand.migrations.12.0.2.0.0.post-migration.migrate", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "cr", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "version", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_brand.migrations.12.0.2.0.0.post-migration._logger", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_brand.models.res_partner_account_brand", "documentation": ["Copyright 2019 ACSONE SA/NV", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_brand.models.res_partner_account_brand.ResPartnerAccountBrand", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_brand.models.res_partner_account_brand.ResPartnerAccountBrand._check_account_type", "asynchronous